metadata.name: 26th Ave, Santa Cruz | 1/10
metadata.description:
Edition 1 of 10.  

-----

Original hand-carved relief of 26th Avenue beach in Santa Cruz, CA. Rubber, ink on paper. October 2022.

Each edition in this collection is a digital scan of a unique physical print.  

-----  
Note: Edition 1 has a thicker border that was reduced before all consecutive editions in this series.
